projects.title: Exchange Explorer
projects.description: Travel advisor app I'm currently building in preparation for my exchange to Copenhagen Business School in January 2023. The app features suggestions of where to visit, eat, and stay based on your current location and also displays the weather for your current location.

projects.title: Gamble Stock Dashboard
projects.description: Multi-functional visual dashboard created using Python and Streamlit for clean data visualization. Dashboards display numerous things including Tweets about stocks from popular traders, mentions of a stock on StockTwits, Plotly candlestick chart of simple technical patterns, and recent mentions of stocks on WallStreetBets.

projects.title: Tempo Discord Bot
projects.description: Discord music bot I created to replace the beloved but discontinued Rhythm bot, built using Discord.js using FFmpeg for streaming

projects.title: williamzhang.dev
projects.description: My personal portfolio built using Gatsby. Used to display information about me, my experiences, my projects, and to provide you an easy way to contact me!

projects.title: Personality Pokedex
projects.description: A Myers-Briggs-esque personality test I made that determine your MBTI type while also likening you to a Pokemon of the same type! One of my earliest projects and for that reason the UI isn't exactly the most polished. In need of a refresh in React!
